           1  f 1   +  1  d i    =  1  f 1 â²           1   f 1  +  f 2  -  d i    +  1  f 2    =  1  f 2 â²         M =    d i   f 1   Â·   f 2    f 1  +  f 2  -  d i            ( 28 )      

