It should be noted that the use of the above technique can facilitate the realization of an arbitrary discrete linear transformation of the form: 
       F â¡  ( k )   =   â  n = 0   N - 1   â¢   f â¡  ( n )   â¢  C â¡  (  k , n  )         ( 65 )      

